<p>There will be space on site for camping and we even have tents and mattresses for people flying in (please ask ahead of time, at least one week before the event). All you need is a sleeping bag!</p>
<p>We&#8217;ll have showers available 5 minutes away in a building with restrained access, as well as on-site bathrooms.</p>
<p>There will not be any food on location outside of the meals that come with registration, so please plan accordingly. The closest supermarket is a short 10-minute drive away (see map).</p>
